Kangtai's pneumococcal vaccine is a welcome addition to India's vaccination schedule. Pneumococcal disease is a leading cause of pneumonia, meningitis, sepsis, and other serious illnesses, particularly in infants and young children. The vaccine is an effective preventive measure against these diseases, reducing the risk of hospitalization and death.
